nodes.text: Supreme Huntress of the United Tribes

Supreme Huntress of the United Tribes, shortened to Supreme Huntress, was a title held by the Togruta queen Elarec Yovet, who as head of state of the Togruta government, also held the titles of Regasa of Shili and Ruler of Togrutas. "Supreme Huntress" was used by the regasa's royal guard as a form of address.
